151
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:51,033
Po svemu sudeci samoubistvo je bilo dogovoreno.

152
00:11:51,100 --> 00:11:52,933
Nekoliko sati pre toga

153
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,700
