Amin.

206
00:13:59,233 --> 00:14:00,867
Amin.

207
00:14:00,933 --> 00:14:02,200
Amin.

208
00:14:05,167 --> 00:14:08,233
Ali za sve nas današnji dan je tužan.

209
00:14:09,367 --> 00:14:12,133
